data.description: **OPEN HOUSE SATURDAY, 18 NOVEMBER 2023** Welcome to your beautiful 4 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom home nestled in the charming neighborhood of Woodlake Meadows. The main level of the home showcases a cozy living room as well as a beautiful kitchen and breakfast bar. Although currently being used as an office space, your formal dining room provides plenty of space for entertaining regardless of how it's set up. Enjoy your main level Master Bedroom and ensuite with a separate shower and Garden tub, dual sinks, and large walk-in closet.   Also on the main level you'll find your laundry room and 2 car garage. As you ascend the staircase, you'll discover a versatile loft area, 3 spacious bedrooms, a full bathroom, and a flex room/media room suitable for all your lounging and movie watching needs.  Outside, a well-maintained yard and covered patio provide the perfect space for outdoor gatherings, barbecues, or simply just enjoying the fresh air.
